  "publisher": "marvel",
  "about": "Wyatt Wingfoot is a fictional supporting character appearing in American comic books published by Marvel Comics.\nWhile having no superpowers, he has spent much time in the company of the Fantastic Four due to his friendship with Human Torch, and his relationship with occasional Fantastic Four member She-Hulk. A Native American of the fictional Keewazi tribe, Wingfoot is an excellent athlete, marksman, hand-to-hand fighter, tracker and animal trainer, and has been of timely help in numerous potentially devastating situations.",
  "note": null,
